===Adjective===
'''no'''

#Used to indicate zero amount or number.
#:''There is no water left.''
#:''No hot dogs were sold yesterday.''
#(''followed by a noun denoting an acitivity'') Used in notices to show that the activity is forbidden.
#:''No smoking''

====Antonyms====
*[[any]]
*[[some]]

